text.description: Created as a project to practice my knowledge. In this web application, the user can search for specific pokemons that appear in the screen. Also, the user can also add pokemons to the pokedex if it chooses to! Have fun using it!
text.tech: React, Styled-Components, Axios, React Hooks, Redux, React Router DOM, Material-UI
